longBusinessSummary: Healthtech Solutions, Inc. engages in the creation and commercialization of cloud-based software for ultrasound scans in the United States. It is also involved in the development of medical therapies for the treatment of disease or injury, such as damage resulting from COVID-19 infection; and acquisition or investment in integrative medical diagnostic or therapeutic software or devices. The company was incorporated in 1985 and is based in New York, New York.
